content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4025.8 - Entrance money not returned

State Regulations

Entrance money is not returned on the death of a horse
nor on the horse's failure to start, whatever the cause of the failure may
be. Notes
